{"link":"ntb.com","html":"<head>\n    <meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n    <meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=edge\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\">\n    <!-- The above 3 meta tags *must* come first in the head; any other head content must come *after* these tags -->\n    <style>\n      .maintenance {\n        margin-top: 10%;\n      }\n      .maintenance_img {\n        margin: 0 auto; \n        display: block; \n        max-width: 100%; \n        height: auto; \n        padding-bottom:30px;\n      }\n      .website {\n        padding-top: 3%; \n        border-top: 1px solid #ccc; \n        margin: 0 26% 3%; \n        font-family: Gotham-Medium,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; \n        font-size: 16px; \n        text-align: center;\n      }\n      .time {\n        margin: 0 auto; \n        text-align: center; \n        font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\n        line-height: 20px; \n        font-size: 14px;\n      }\n      .mailus {\n        text-decoration: none; \n        outline: 0; \n        color: #206b8c; \n        display:block;\n      }\n      .logo {\n        width:148px;\n        height:39px;\n        margin: 0 auto 30px; \n        display: block; \n        cursor: pointer;\n        background:url('data:image/png;base64,') no-repeat center;\n      }\n      @media only screen and (max-width: 767px) {\n        .maintenance_img {\n          display:none;\n        }\n        .maintenance {\n          margin-top: 35%;\n        }\n        .website {\n          padding-top: 3%; \n          border-top: none; \n          margin: 0 10% 8%; \n        }\n      }\n\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"maintenance\" onload=\"scheduleTimer();\">\n\t<a role=\"logo\" aria-label=\"TireKingdom Service Center Logo\" class=\"logo\" onclick=\"newLocation()\"></a>\n\t<h5 class=\"website\">Our website is down for scheduled maintenance</h5>\n\t<div class=\"time\">\n\t\t<p>We will be back <span id=\"time\">in 2:30:00</span></p>\n\t\t<p>If you need assistance,</p>\n\t\t<p>call 1-800-741-7261</p>\n\t\t<a class=\"mailus\" href=\"mailto:web@tbccorp.com\">Email Us</a>\n\t\t<a class=\"mailus\" href=\"http://www.tirekingdom.accountonline.com\">Manage your Credit Card</a>\n\t</div>\n\n  \n  <script src=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/moment.js/2.15.2/moment.min.js\"></script>\n  <script src=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/moment-timezone/0.5.9/moment-timezone-with-data-2010-2020.min.js\"></script>\n  \n  <script>\n  (function() {\n    //Everything is handled in 24hr format. Do not change. AM/PM adds confusion.\n    var opts = {\n          maintStartTime: { // 1:30am\n            h: 1,\n            m: 30\n          },\n          maintEndTime: {   // 4:30am\n            h: 4,\n            m: 30\n          },\n          serverTimeZone: 'America/New_York', // EST\n          timeFormat: 'HH.mm'                 // 24 hour format separated by dot\n        }, \n        durationSeconds = 0;\n\n    function timeInMaintenanceRange(serverTime) {\n      return Number(opts.maintStartTime.h + '.' + opts.maintStartTime.m) <= serverTime && Number(opts.maintEndTime.h + '.' + opts.maintEndTime.m) >= serverTime;\n    }\n\n    function scheduleTimer() {\n      // Initialize\n      var durationHours;\n      var durationMinutes;\n      var serverTime = moment().tz(opts.serverTimeZone).format(opts.timeFormat);\n      var serverTimeNumber = Number(serverTime);\n      var serverHours = Number(serverTime.split('.')[0]);\n      var serverMinutes = Number(serverTime.split('.')[1]);\n\n      if (timeInMaintenanceRange(serverTimeNumber)) {\n        durationHours = opts.maintEndTime.h - serverHours;\n        durationMinutes = opts.maintEndTime.m - serverMinutes;\n        durationSeconds = ((durationHours * 60) + durationMinutes) * 60;\n        doTimer();\n      }\n    }\n\n    function doTimer() {\n      var hours = Math.floor(durationSeconds / 3600);\n      var time = durationSeconds - (hours * 3600);\n      var minutes = Math.floor(time / 60);\n      var seconds = time - (minutes * 60);\n\n      document.getElementById('time').innerHTML = 'in ' + hours + ':' + (minutes > 9 ? minutes : '0' + minutes ) + ':' + (seconds > 9 ? seconds : '0' + seconds );\n      if (--durationSeconds >= 0) {\n        setTimeout(doTimer, 1000);\n      } else {\n        window.location.href = 'https://' + window.location.hostname;\n      }\n    }\n    \n    function newLocation() { \n      var url = window.location.hostname;\n      window.location.href = 'https://' + url;\n    }\n\n    window.scheduleTimer = scheduleTimer;\n  })();\n</script>\n\n<script>\n  function newLocation() { \n    var url = window.location.hostname;\n    window.location.href = 'https://' + url;\n  }\n</script>\n\n\n\n</body>"}
